  "body_html": "<p><span>A royal blend of </span><strong data-start=\"129\" data-end=\"164\">juicy pear, peach, and mandarin</strong><span> wrapped in a heart of </span><strong data-start=\"187\" data-end=\"216\">rose, peony, and magnolia</strong><span>, resting on a warm base of </span><strong data-start=\"244\" data-end=\"274\">vanilla, praline, and musk</strong><span>.</span><br data-start=\"275\" data-end=\"278\"><span>It’s </span><strong data-start=\"283\" data-end=\"327\">elegant, feminine, and effortlessly chic</strong><span> — the kind of scent that makes you feel like the </span><em data-start=\"377\" data-end=\"393\">main character</em><span>. </span></p>\n<p data-start=\"221\" data-end=\"343\">✨ <strong data-start=\"223\" data-end=\"232\">Vibe:</strong><br data-start=\"232\" data-end=\"235\">Sophisticated, confident, and romantic — a powdery floral blend that feels timeless and effortlessly chic.</p>\n<p data-start=\"345\" data-end=\"566\">💐 <strong data-start=\"348\" data-end=\"365\">When to wear:</strong><br data-start=\"365\" data-end=\"368\">Perfect for <strong data-start=\"380\" data-end=\"396\">day or night</strong>, it can be both your <strong data-start=\"418\" data-end=\"437\">signature scent</strong> and an <strong data-start=\"445\" data-end=\"465\">everyday perfume</strong>. Ideal for romantic evenings, special occasions, or anytime you want to feel beautifully feminine.</p>",
